{"word":"H7411 - רָמָה - râmâh - raw-maw' - Beguile","slug":"H7411","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָמָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râmâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-maw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Beguile"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05DE;&#x05D4; - ra&#x0302;ma&#x0302;h</b> - <i>raw-maw'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>hurl</i>; specifically to <i>shoot</i>; figuratively to <i>delude</i> or <i>betray</i> (as if causing to fall): - beguile, betray, [bow-] man, carry, deceive, throw."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4820\">H4820</a>, <a href=\"#/H7423\">H7423</a>, <a href=\"#/H8649\">H8649</a>"}]}